## Day 2 Features Implemented âœ…

### File Upload System
- Avatar upload functionality with validation
- 2MB file size limit
- Supported formats: JPEG, PNG, GIF, WEBP
- Unique filename generation
- Old file cleanup

### Email Notification System
- Welcome email for new users
- HTML email templates with Thymeleaf
- Gmail SMTP configuration
- Error handling for email failures

### New API Endpoints
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Access |
|--------|----------|-------------|---------|
| POST | `/api/files/upload-avatar` | Upload user avatar | Authenticated |
| GET | `/api/files/avatar/{filename}` | Serve avatar image | Public |

### Configuration
- File storage properties
- Email service configuration
- Multipart file upload settings
